  <div class="views-field views-field-created">        <span class="field-content">Wednesday, December 16, 2015 - 3:07pm</span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p><img height="494" width="400" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="media-element file-default" typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://writers.ns.ca/sites/default/files/booktree.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>The WFNS office will be closed at 11 AM on Friday, December 18th and will reopen on Monday, January 4th at 9 AM. </strong></p>
<p>We wish you all a joy-filled, book-filled and writing time-filled holiday season!</p>
<p>See you in 2016! </p>
