  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="/blog/wfns-hal-con.html">WFNS at Hal-Con!</a></span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-created">        <span class="field-content">Tuesday, October 27, 2015 - 10:40am</span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>We're blasting off to Hal-Con Science Fiction and Fantasy Convention from October 30 - November 1 in Halifax. We'll have signings by Sherry D. Ramsey, Cynthia d'Entremont, BR Myers and Kat Kruger. If you're attending the con, drop by and say hello! We'll be in the vendor area of the Scotiabank Centre at F7!</p>
<p>In addition to chatting with potential new members about what we do, we'll also have a series of author signings:</p>
<p><strong>Friday, October 30</strong><br />3 - 4 PM - Kat Kruger<br />5 -6 PM - Sherry D. Ramsey</p></div>  </div>  
  



  
